{"tid":497611,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"去完working holiday後去同學聚會，冇面再出黎見面","createTime":"2017-12-13T03:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T11:45:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":18,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6403832b029ab490424a94ab225e908c5559f5e4","tid":497611,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"我早幾年岩岩HD畢業，身邊好多人決定去做野，而我冇做野，繼續讀TOP UP DEGREE，FULL-TIME讀咗一年，畢業之後都冇開始正式做嘢，去左澳洲做working holiday兩年，最返先返黎香港做野。我以為有個DEGREE實冇死，點知好多僱主都因為我冇工作經驗，加埋市道一般，壓價壓得好勁，搞到我得$10000一個月。咁啱最近班同學話搞聚會，我去咗，發現原來三年之間，佢哋已經升晒職，搵緊$20000~$32000不等，得我一個咁霉，搞到我真係好自卑，以後唔敢再出席"},{"pid":"2e24198dcd986ce5790702c84a31772709d3f62a","tid":497611,"uid":95504,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"起碼你嘅人生同人哋唔同"},{"pid":"10ab715990b079f57fff6ce7faff9d775db64fa8","tid":497611,"uid":33338,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"屌 無睇名"},{"pid":"2d2d97875c7dc25e4a0917a42b907ea05410083e","tid":497611,"uid":1977,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:18:30.000Z","msg":"仲以為你聚會果陣溜屎"},{"pid":"9e27f1be08c847a6ff5d7e375d37c5d10ad58ff0","tid":497611,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:25:01.000Z","msg":"Ching同我差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c9b2cb14d3c90356db063ee552e876fce03a9a","tid":497611,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以為你聚會果陣溜屎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0691396b7f0e4f74625ac38cbbfa9aa7cf28b2db","tid":497611,"uid":142544,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:39:58.000Z","msg":"依度都冇人月入低過50K"},{"pid":"2e273989a504768cd12871d22143d4ad620ce1f1","tid":497611,"uid":63588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:38:15.000